<div class="paragraph">
<p>shopping24.de is a subsidiary of the Otto Group and an online portal for price and product comparisons. In order to set up the billiger.de plugin in plentymarkets, you have to register with <a href="https://www.s24.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">shopping24.de</a>&nbsp;<span class="icon "><i class="fa fa-external-link  "></i></span> first. Please note that this website is currently only available in German.</p>
</div>
</div>
